<div id="review_742680234" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/742680234" />
    <a title="Richard" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/6014887-richard"><img alt="Richard" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1389632385p2/6014887.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/742680234?book_show_action=true">Oct 16, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Richard" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Richard" href="/user/show/6014887-richard">Richard</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 0143012312" href="/book/show/6482842-hateship-friendship-courtship-loveship-marriage">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6014887-richard?shelf=reviewed">reviewed</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6014887-richard?shelf=short-stories">short-stories</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6014887-richard?shelf=2013">2013</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6014887-richard?shelf=nobel-prize-winners">nobel-prize-winners</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6014887-richard?shelf=canada">canada</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6014887-richard?shelf=by-women">by-women</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer742680234" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8346158042658008544">This collection of stories by Alice Munro is typical of much of her work. The stories are populated by people leading what looks on the surface like humdrum lives. But just underneath the surface, strange feelings boil, ready to erupt when events occur which make this possible. Munro has a lot of knowledge about the various types of relationships between men and women, how they can be built, twisted, broken and remade. These are not happy stories--in fact, some of them are disturbing. But the na</span>
  <span id="freeText8346158042658008544" style="display:none">This collection of stories by Alice Munro is typical of much of her work. The stories are populated by people leading what looks on the surface like humdrum lives. But just underneath the surface, strange feelings boil, ready to erupt when events occur which make this possible. Munro has a lot of knowledge about the various types of relationships between men and women, how they can be built, twisted, broken and remade. These are not happy stories--in fact, some of them are disturbing. But the narration is powerful, and the author seems always to know exactly what effect she will produce.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8346158042658008544" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
